(1, 1, 'faqs', 'FAQs', '<p>The FMCG (Fast-moving consumer goods) industry is one of the oldest and most established industries in the world. It is typically characterized by its highly competitive landscape and consumer orientation.</p><div class="list-group"><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">I want to subscribe to VENDIS Sales Force Automation. How do I subscribe?</h5></div><small>Please send us e-mail, we will follow up with more information and data we require to run VENDIS SFA</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">Which type of business this platform is specifically meant for?</h5></div><small>VENDIS is for Enterprises with mobile Work Force (Field Sales Team, Field Technicians, Drivers), VENDIS provides data management solutions that enable Mobility, Transparency, Efficiency, Accuracy by tracking events and transactions</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">How much time is needed for deployment?</h5></div><small>You can start pilot or proof of concept within a week. For larger deployment, it will take at least 2 or 3 weeks to get early VENDIS deployment</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">How can I save my money? How is VENDIS cost-effective?</h5></div><small>VENDIS is a cost-effective solution for your business and it is based on subscription per user per month. For more information, you can reach us at sales@vendisservice.com and our product experts will contact you and help you</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">Will this application work on as low a bandwidth as 2G/3G connection?</h5></div><small>Yes, it works smoothly on 2G and 3G</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">Is there a GPS relevant reporting available? If so, can I track my sales force?</h5></div><small>We do have GPS relevant reporting, we do support tracking of sales force movement. GPS is captured every 5, 10 or 15 mins and when a transaction is carried out in the field</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">Do I need an infrastructure?</h5></div><small>No, you do not need an infrastructure. The app runs on your mobile and hence, you can effortlessly monitor your business on your device.</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">Do I need any additional hardware?</h5></div><small>No server hardware is required. VENDIS is available in a secure cloud option with a subscription-based fee. In-field users will require a smartphone device with data connection.</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">Do I have an on premise option of deploying VENDIS?</h5></div><small>Yes. The option is available to all customers with more than 50 users.</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">I would like to host the app on my server. Is it possible ?</h5></div><small>It is possible to have an on-premise hosting of VENDIS. Our team members will have to deploy it and help you with regular upkeep. We can remotely install VENDIS.</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">In case of an event where I may have to call you after the stipulated working hours, would it be possible that I get you over the phone?</h5></div><small>Customized 24X7 support option is available only to enterprise customers. Default support is available during business hours on Monday to Friday.</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">Is there any backup for all the data?</h5></div><small>Yes. Data is backed up on daily basis. In case, client has accidently deleted some data, selective of holistic backup restore can be performed on request by our deployment team.</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">What happens to my data on the device which gets stolen?</h5></div><small>VENDIS only stores data temporarily on smartphones whenever there is no internet connection. VENDIS will clean up all data as soon as VENDIS application has internet connection</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">What if I want to stop using VENDIS app? Will it still store all my data?</h5></div><small>Customers can download all relevant data by themselves. VENDIS is available in display and data download mode for 10 days after expiry of the subscription.</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">What if while working online my network drops?</h5></div><small>Most of the transactional functionalities in VENDIS are designed for offline mode, which means users can continue to work when network drops or when there is no network signal at all.</small></a><a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start" href="#"><div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between"><h5 class="mb-1">We have our own ERP system. Can VENDIS be integrated with our ERP system?</h5></div><small>Yes. VENDIS already comes with ready-to-go content for SAP integration. It also offers APIs for integration with other ERPs. VENDIS is designed on service oriented architecture based on SOAP standards, which allows for graceful and secure integration with any other system.</small></a></div>', 'FAQs', NULL, '2017-10-11 15:25:16', '2017-10-17 20:52:23', '2017-10-17 20:52:23'),
(2, 1, 'pricing', 'Pricing', '<h2 class="title">Simple Pricing, Easy Setup, No Surprises</h2><div class="table-responsive"><table class="table table-bordered"><thead><tr><th><br></th><th>Features</th><th>Monitoring &amp; Tracking</th><th>Basic SFA</th><th>Enterprise SFA</th><th>Premium SFA</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td rowspan="2"><strong>Work</strong></td><td>Attendance</td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td>Position Tracking</td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="2"><strong>Route Performance</strong></td><td>Automated Route Management</td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td>Visit Management and Tracking</td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="6"><strong>Transaction</strong></td><td>Taking Order</td><td><br></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td>Check Credit Limit</td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td>Check Inventory</td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><i class="fa fa-check-circle" style="color: #24cc71"></i></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td>Check outstanding Invoices</td><td><br></td><td><br></td><td><i cl